This is Perl module WWW::Shorten::Durl.

INSTALLATION

WWW::Shorten::Durl installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan WWW::Shorten::Durl

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

WWW::Shorten::Durl documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc WWW::Shorten::Durl

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

JEEN
